OL,4,Ctwo colleagues in a hospital
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for 30 years
OL,7,Fafter stabbing two colleagues with a
OL,8,Fpickaxe at his hospital.
OL,10,FMatteo Bottarelli, 44, was sentenced
OL,11,Fat Wood Green Court and will serve
OL,12,Fmost of his sentence in custody.
OL,14,FIn June 2023 police were called to
OL,15,FCentral Middlesex Hospital to reports
OL,16,Fthat two people had been stabbed.
OL,18,FOfficers found two men, aged in their
OL,19,F40s, both suffering from significant
OL,20,Finjuries.
