OL,6,FAlthough substantial, their injuries
OL,7,Fwere not life threatening. Moments
OL,8,Fbefore the attack Bottarelli had
OL,9,Fapproached one of his colleagues at
OL,10,Fthe hospital saying "today is your
OL,11,Flucky day."
OL,13,FHe then attempted to attack a male
OL,14,Fmember of staff, before attacking two
OL,15,Fmore male staff members with a pickaxe
OL,16,Fand a scalpel.
