OL,6,FAn urgent search was carried out and
OL,7,Farmed officers found Bottarelli at his
OL,8,Fhome. He was arrested and taken to
OL,9,Fhospital for treatment to self-
OL,10,Finflicted injuries.
OL,12,FTrevor MacGuire, 61, from
OL,13,FWaterlooville was one of three victims
OL,14,Fattacked by Matteo Bottarelli, he has
OL,15,Fa lifelong brain injury as a result of
OL,16,Fhead injuries caused by the attack.
