OL,6,FHe said: "I feel incredible sadness,
OL,7,Fit was all unnecessary, the actions of
OL,8,FMatteo Bottarelli has caused so much
OL,9,Fpain and complexity for everyone
OL,10,Finvolved. There is only one life
OL,11,Fsentence here which is mine and I have
OL,12,Fto live these injuries".
OL,14,FDetective Constable Jacob Eyres, from
OL,15,Fthe Met's North West Command, said:
OL,16,F"We have worked hard to build a case
OL,17,Fagainst Bottarelli who posed a clear
OL,18,Fthreat to his work colleagues and to
OL,19,Fpublic safety.
