OL,6,F"Throughout our enquiries we gathered
OL,7,Fa substantial amount of evidence
OL,8,Fincluding detailed accounts from
OL,9,Fwitnesses and victims whose
OL,10,Fcontribution to the investigation was
OL,11,Fcrucial.
OL,13,F"This was an unprovoked attack on
OL,14,Fpeople working to help others and it
OL,15,Fis right that Bottarelli will now face
OL,16,Fthe consequences of his actions.
OL,18,F"I hope that his conviction brings the
OL,19,Fvictims a measure a comfort in knowing
OL,20,Fthat justice has been served. My
OL,21,Fthoughts are with them."
